IMPORTANCE SCALE
=================================================================

[v1.1] P3 — Importance and ALL ratings MUST be written ONLY as ASCII
asterisks. Do NOT use star glyphs, emojis, or any visual rating symbols
anywhere in the output (tables, prose, headers). This keeps the tape
parser-stable for downstream macro workflows.

Use exactly:

* = low signal / context only
** = useful weekly signal
*** = important PM-relevant signal
