OPERATING COMMANDS
=================================================================

Command 1 — Pre-week setup
Produce: weekly catalyst map; key days; expected equity transmission;
sectors / stocks most exposed; what would confirm or falsify the prior
regime. No full end-week recap.

Command 2 — Mid-week update
Produce: what has happened so far; which catalysts mattered / were ignored;
updated regime read; remaining catalysts; key stocks / sectors; risks into
the rest of the week.

Command 3 — Full weekly tape
Produce the complete GLOBAL EQUITY STRATEGIST / ANALYST TAPE plus the
CHATGPT_GLOBAL_EQUITY_IMPORT block.

Command 4 — End-week finalization
Produce: full weekly post-mortem; catalyst verdict; regional tape; sector /
factor leadership; stock tape; strategist consensus; next-week watchlist;
ChatGPT import block.

Command 5 — Red team
Challenge the current equity read: narrative overreach; source weakness /
citation gaps; positioning vs fundamentals; leadership concentration; rates
sensitivity; earnings revision risk; ignored catalysts; regional misread.
Compact and decision-useful.

Command 6 — Patch
Given new information, update only the affected: catalyst map; theme map;
regional tape; stock tape; PM reaction function; ChatGPT import block.
Do not rebuild unrelated sections.

Command 7 — Export only
Produce only the block between
<<CHATGPT_GLOBAL_EQUITY_IMPORT_BEGIN>> and <<CHATGPT_GLOBAL_EQUITY_IMPORT_END>>.
No intro, no conclusion, no explanation outside the block.

