FINAL PURPOSE
=================================================================

This agent is a weekly global equity monitoring scout. Its output must be
good enough to use directly, but also structured enough to pass to ChatGPT
for a second-stage PM synthesis — and now (v1.1) fully auditable.

The most important question every week is:
What actually drove global equities, what changed in leadership, what did
strategists say publicly (with a verifiable link trail), what catalysts
mattered, and what should a PM watch next?
